OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FA "long-standing, committed jihadist"
OL,7,Fwho planned a terror attack on a
OL,8,Fmilitary site with a man who went on
OL,9,Fto commit a fatal knife attack at a
OL,10,FManchester synagogue, has been jailed
OL,11,Ffor 17 years.
OL,13,FMohammed Bashir, 31, drove Jihad Al-
OL,14,FShamie on a 10-hour round trip to
OL,15,Fconduct hostile reconnaissance at the
OL,16,FUK Defence Academy in Swindon,
OL,17,FWiltshire, on 14 August 2025 before
OL,18,Fthey deliberately disposed of their
OL,19,Fmobile phones.
OL,26,@nD@COUnD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FLess than two months later, Al-Shamie,
OL,7,F35, was shot dead by police on 2
OL,8,FOctober while he carried out his
OL,9,Fterrorist attack at the Heaton Park
OL,10,FHebrew Congregation synagogue in which
OL,11,Ftwo worshippers were killed.
OL,13,FProsecutors say there was no evidence
OL,14,Fto suggest the defendant had any
OL,15,Finvolvement in the Heaton Park
OL,16,Fincident, but the planned attack on
OL,17,Fthe defence facility was similar in
OL,18,Fnature and would have caused multiple
OL,19,Ffatalities.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FIn June 2026, Bashir, of Cheetham
OL,7,FHill, Manchester, pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fthe preparation of terrorist acts.
OL,10,FMoD Shrivenham is the home of the UK's
OL,11,FDefence Academy, the court heard,
OL,12,Fwhich provides professional defence
OL,13,Fand security education to the British
OL,14,Farmed forces, wider UK government, UK
OL,15,Findustry and overseas personnel.
OL,17,FRoutinely, there will be up to 4,000
OL,18,Fstaff, contractors, students and
OL,19,Fvisitors on site at any given time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FSentencing Bashir on 23 July, Mrs
OL,7,FJustice Cheema-Grubb told him that by
OL,8,FAugust 2025 he had become a "firmly
OL,9,Fcommitted jihadist" and together with
OL,10,FAl-Shamie was "equally engaged" in
OL,11,Fplanning an attack on a British
OL,12,Fmilitary target "in which you and he
OL,13,Fexpected to kill and be killed".
OL,15,FShe rejected his claim to a probation
OL,16,Fofficer that he no longer held
OL,17,Fextremist views and regretted his
OL,18,Factions.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@SO]rD@OOUrD@_O]tD@QOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FThe judge said: "I consider you remain
OL,7,Fdangerous. You have given no grounds
OL,8,Fthat your attitude has really changed
OL,9,Fat all."
OL,11,FFollowing sentencing, Manchester-born
OL,12,FBashir, who also holds a Pakistani
OL,13,Fpassport, smiled to family members in
OL,14,Fthe upper public gallery of the
OL,15,Fcourtroom as he casually walked from
OL,16,Fthe dock.
OL,26,@nD@QOUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
