PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FBashir, who also holds a Pakistani
OL,7,Fpassport and has no previous
OL,8,Fconvictions, was arrested at
OL,9,FManchester Airport on 27 November 2025
OL,10,Fbut was not charged in relation to the
OL,11,Fsynagogue attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FFollowing the attack, WhatsApp
OL,7,Fmessages and voice note exchanges
OL,8,Fbetween the pair were uncovered when
OL,9,Fpolice analysed two phones seized from
OL,10,FAl-Shamie from when he was arrested
OL,11,Feight months earlier in February 2025
OL,12,Fover an alleged breach of a non-
OL,13,Fmolestation order and in September
OL,14,F2025 when he was held on suspicion of
OL,15,Frape, Manchester Crown Court heard.
OL,17,FIt has now been revealed that Al-
OL,18,FShamie's phones were not examined by
OL,19,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
