OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FThe Chief Constable of Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police (GMP) has issued a
OL,8,Fformal apology, describing the force
OL,9,Ffailings as a "missed opportunity" to
OL,10,Funcover evidence of his "extremist
OL,11,Fmindset" before he went on a knife
OL,12,Frampage.
OL,14,FMelvin Cravitz, 66, and Adrian Daulby,
OL,15,F53, died after Al-Shamie, a Syrian-
OL,16,Fborn UK citizen, drove his Kia Picanto
OL,17,Finto the gates of the synagogue and
OL,18,Fbegan attacking with a knife, wearing
OL,19,Fa fake suicide belt.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FProsecutors said both men were
OL,7,Fmotivated by their anti-Semitic views
OL,8,Fin targeting the defence base, and
OL,9,Fthat Al-Shamie had made several
OL,10,Finternet searches for IDF (Israel
OL,11,FDefense Forces) soldiers training in
OL,12,FBritain.
OL,14,FFrom late August 2025, the attentions
OL,15,Fof Al-Shamie appeared to turn to the
OL,16,FHeaton Park synagogue, the court was
OL,17,Ftold, with searches relating to that
OL,18,Flocation and people associated with it
OL,19,Fsuch as local rabbis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1784805503
OL,3,C'Jihadist' jailed for separate terror
OL,4,Cplot with Manchester synagogue attacker
OL,6,FHe also looked online for meat
OL,7,Fcleavers and "travel bags for them",
OL,8,Ffollowed by a search on 22 September
OL,9,Ffor "yom kippur massacre of nature".
OL,11,FAl-Shamie went on to stab one man to
OL,12,Fdeath at the Heaton Park synagogue and
OL,13,Finjured three others, the court heard,
OL,14,Fwhile a stray bullet from police
OL,15,Fstruck and killed another man.
OL,17,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,18,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,19,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,20,Four region.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@cO]qD@EOUqD@cO]
